  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><u>Inghams Named A Which? Recommended Travel Company</u></strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/travel-agents/article/travel-agents/the-best-and-worst-travel-agents"></a><a href="https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/travel-agents/article/travel-agents/the-best-and-worst-travel-agents"><strong><u><img style="width: 141px; height: 113px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13078511/holiday-companies-july-2019-which-logo.jpg?width=141&amp;height=113&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/148d80ef8f184ef7b86c46a3e030d03e" /></u></strong></a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays">Inghams</a> is delighted to have been awarded the <strong>Which? Recommended Provider </strong>status, following <a href="https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/travel-agents/article/travel-agents/the-best-and-worst-travel-agents">a review of its services</a> by consumer champion Which?.</p>
<p>Inghams gained the recognition following a Which? survey of UK holidaymakers on the services offered by package holiday providers, and as a result of performing well in the additional expert analysis. When its <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Summer</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a> programmes were judged on various aspects such as their quality of accommodation, customer service and value for money, Inghams - which this year celebrates its 85<sup>th</sup> year in business - achieved a high score of 90%, granting it status as a Which? Recommended Provider.</p>
<p>Paul Carter, Inghams CEO, says: “I am absolutely thrilled to share the good news that Inghams has been named a Which? Recommended Travel Company. People’s holidays are precious and, now more so than ever, people are looking for unforgettable holiday experiences that don’t cost the earth. On our 85<sup>th</sup> birthday, we’re very proud to look back on our decades’ worth of expertise and experience in providing outstanding holiday experiences, and I’d like to thank all our staff and partners, based both here in the UK and overseas, for their unwavering commitment to delivering an exceptional service at great value. We also thank our loyal guests for choosing Inghams and we look forward to another 85 years of providing fantastic holidays!”</p>
<p><u>What is a Which? Recommended Provider?</u>           <u><br /></u>Each month, Which? analyses and reviews services across a range of industries, including financial, insurance, broadband and hospitality. Their researchers set strict minimal standards for these services and Which? speaks to UK consumers to make sure they rate highly. Only the best performers will receive a Which? Recommended Provider endorsement.</p>
<p><strong>-ENDS-</strong></p>
<p><strong><u>ABOUT INGHAMS:</u></strong><strong>                                <u><br /></u></strong>Inghams was founded by Walter Ingham in 1934, born out of his enduring passion for ski, mountaineering and walking. In 2019, Inghams celebrates its 85<sup>th</sup> year in business and the brand continues to pride itself on being one of the UK's leading, most experienced specialist tour operators, delivering a wide range of award-winning holidays to its loyal guests. Today, Inghams offers <u><a data-udi="umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25e767db044444389ae09383681f982e}" title="Ski Holidays">winter holidays</a></u> to over 90 resorts in eight countries, with flights from 21 UK regional airports. It also has a popular <u><a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Lakes &amp; Mountains</a></u> summer holiday programme to many European destinations and a dedicated <u><a data-udi="umb://document/4483b219b1754b70910d3f01f05be9be" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4483b219b1754b70910d3f01f05be9be}" title="Italy Holidays">Inghams Italy</a></u> programme. For more information, visit <u><a data-udi="umb://document/b49585f93afa4fa9bb0bf506c7aa71da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b49585f93afa4fa9bb0bf506c7aa71da}" title="Home">www.inghams.co.uk</a></u>. </p>]]></bodyText>
